Muchidzidzo [[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[Chikunguru]] (cylinder in English) zvinoreva chiumbwa chine [[uso]] huviri hwakati sambamba, nuso hwechitatu hune [[mucheko]] wedenderedzwa. Chikunguru ndiwo muenzaniso  we[[zhumwi]] redenderedzwa.

Chikunguru chiumbwa  chinokunguruka zviri nyore uye chichifamba nenzira yakatwasuka pachinokunguruka. Kunze kwe[[urungano]] zvimwe zviumbwa zvine [[mumbu]] hazvikwanise kukunguruka nenzira yakatwasuka. Shoko reEnglish rokuti ‘’cylinder rinobva kuLatin richireva something which rolls’’.


Muenzaniso we[[chikunguru]] unowanikwa:  pa[[mugoro]] unotakuriswa mvura; paipi dzemvura; zvidziro zve’’Kitchen’’ kuma[[ruwa]] zvichingodaro. Nekumwe kuuna vhiri rakaumbwa se[[chikunguru]] chine [[hwasha]] hudiki pane [[pimadanho]].
